---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const currentPath = Astro.url.pathname;
const lang = 'en';

const title = 'Syaiful Anam Journey - Continuous Learning & Builder';
const description = 'Follow my journey from multi-talented designer to tech entrepreneur, supported by amazing mentors and continuous learning philosophy.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} lang={lang}>
	<div class="container">
		<Header currentPath={currentPath} lang={lang} />

		<main class="main-content">
			<div class="journey-content">
				<h1 style="text-align: center;">My Journey</h1>

				<p class="intro">
					This isn't just a career journeyâ€”this is the story of how I
					was discovered by extraordinary people who saw more than just technical ability.
					Each phase is a life chapter that transformed me, shaped my character, and showed that
					with the right mentors and unlimited desire to learn, anything is possible.
				</p>

				<div class="timeline">
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<div class="timeline-marker">1</div>
						<div class="timeline-content">
							<h2>First Job</h2>
				<div class="timeline-period">January 1, 2017 - October 8, 2020</div>
							<div class="story-highlight">
								<p>
									<em>"That interview changed everything. Ian Darmawan didn't just see my resumeâ€”
									he saw potential I hadn't even realized myself."</em>
								</p>
							</div>
							<p>
								My professional journey at Gravcode Studio wasn't coincidenceâ€”it was destiny.
								Starting in December 2016 during the internship proposal, Ian Darmawan saw something deeper than technical capabilities.
								I officially started interning on January 1, 2017, and after 2 months of proving myself, I was hired as a Junior Designer in March 2017.
								That was the beginning of a transformation I never expectedâ€”delving into visual communication fundamentals with CorelDRAW, understanding how design speaks and influences perception.
							</p>
							<p>
								Gravcode Studio saw beyond my design capabilities. In December 2018, trust came againâ€”I was entrusted to lead IT Support, opening up the technical world completely.
								Parallel to that, I also developed WordPress developer skills, building dynamic websites for hundreds of clients that integrated client needs with web technology.
								Every troubleshooting session was a valuable lesson about how systems work, how users think, and how simple solutions can transform productivity.
								By June 2019, I stepped into Assistant System Analystâ€”no longer just fixing problems, but understanding why they occurred, analyzing workflows, and seeing the bigger picture of technology and business.
							</p>
							<p>
								October 8, 2020 became the moment I decided to leave and grow.
								Each role didn't just enhance my technical skills, but also shaped my perspectiveâ€”from visual-thinking designer to logical technical support to systematic system analyst.
								All working together to create a strong foundation for the entrepreneurial career ahead.
							</p>

							<p>Huge thank you to my extraordinary mentors: <a href="https://id.linkedin.com/in/agustino-sidabutar-b8a079141" target="_blank">Agustino Sidabutar</a>, <a href="https://id.linkedin.com/in/ian-darmawan/" target="_blank">Ian Darmawan</a>, <a href="https://id.linkedin.com/in/yonathan-japri-65143585" target="_blank">Yonathan Japri</a>, and <a href="https://id.linkedin.com/in/rendiana-p-721327145" target="_blank">Rendiana P.</a> as well as to all friends: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/shierlydista/" target="_blank">Shierly</a>, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/mrgien/" target="_blank">Rizqi</a>, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/haristabdurrachman/" target="_blank">Harits</a>, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/dinaroktarini/" target="_blank">Dinar</a>, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/aprillia_zees/" target="_blank">April</a>, <a href="https://www.instagram.com/heniwahyn/" target="_blank">Heni</a>, and <a href="https://www.instagram.com/chayoo_zen/" target="_blank">Zen</a> who have been part of this journey.</p>

							<div class="story-highlight">
								<p>
									<em>"Every farewell is the beginning of a new chapter. October 8, 2020 wasn't an end, but the gateway to greater growth."</em>
								</p>
							</div>

							<div class="education-section">
								<h3>Education</h3>
								<div class="education-timeline">
									<div class="education-item">
										<div class="education-period">2013 - 2016</div>
										<div class="education-content">
											<h4>SMAN 16 Surabaya</h4>
											<p>Science</p>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div class="education-item">
										<div class="education-period">2016 - 2017</div>
										<div class="education-content">
											<h4>Magistra Utama</h4>
											<p>Informatics Engineering and Web Design</p>
										</div>
									</div>
									<div class="education-item">
										<div class="education-period">2018 - 2022</div>
										<div class="education-content">
											<h4>Universitas 17 Agustus 1945 (Untag)</h4>
											<p>Informatics Engineering</p>
										</div>
									</div>
								</div>
								<p class="education-note">While working at Gravcode Studio, I pursued formal education to strengthen my technical foundation.</p>
							</div>

							<div class="tools-grid">
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="CorelDRAW" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>CorelDRAW</span>
								</div>
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="Photoshop" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>Photoshop</span>
								</div>
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="Illustrator" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>Illustrator</span>
								</div>
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="InDesign" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>InDesign</span>
								</div>
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="WordPress" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>WordPress</span>
								</div>
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="HTML" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>HTML</span>
								</div>
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="CSS" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>CSS</span>
								</div>
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="JavaScript" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>JavaScript</span>
								</div>
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="PHP" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>PHP</span>
								</div>
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="MySQL" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>MySQL</span>
								</div>
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="Git" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>Git</span>
								</div>
								<div class="tool-item">
									<img src="/images/tech/astro.svg" alt="GitHub" width="32" height="32" />
									<span>GitHub</span>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="timeline-item">
						<div class="timeline-marker">2</div>
						<div class="timeline-content">
							<h2>Entrepreneur Journey</h2>
										<div class="story-highlight">
								<p>
									<em>"Sometimes destiny comes in the form of a website project. A CEO with extraordinary vision
									didn't just see my workâ€”he saw the future we could build together.
									One year later, that trust transformed into a lifetime opportunity."</em>
								</p>
							</div>
							<p>
								Meeting Pak Budi wasn't just business. It started when Vido Garment wanted to create a website at Gravcode Studio,
								but that 1-hour demonstration opened doors I never imagined.
								A year later, there were no more talks about projectsâ€”only discussions about dreams,
								visions, and how technology could transform industries.
							</p>

							<p>
								<strong>October 9, 2020</strong>, I accepted Pak Budi's offer to join the team, and <strong>October 13, 2020</strong> officially joined.
								This period was filled with many discussions about Vido Garment and the formation of Digital360 concept.
								<strong>November 27, 2020</strong>, purchasing the Digital360.id domain became the gateway to the tech entrepreneur era, starting to build digital solutions from scratch.
							</p>

							<p>
								This journey not only developed my technical skills, but also built my entrepreneurial mindset.
								From development expertise to business insights, from problem solving to strategic thinking.
								All of this has formed a solid foundation for leading Digital360 and integrating technology into Fabrik Group.
							</p>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

			
				<div class="conclusion">
					<h2>The Next Journey?</h2>
					<p>
						From designing visual to building systems, from serving hundreds of clients to leading technology companies.
						Every step opens new insights about how technology can transform industries.
						From WordPress developer to AI-driven builder, from technical support to strategic entrepreneur.
						The next chapter is being written, with technology and mentors as faithful companions.
					</p>
					<br>
					<div class="story-highlight">
					<p>
						<em>"This journey is just the beginning of a much greater chapter."</em>
					</p>
				</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer lang={lang} />
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.main-content {
		min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
	}

	.journey-content {
		padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
	}

	.intro {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.timeline {
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
	}

	.timeline::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		top: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		width: 2px;
		background-color: var(--color-border);
	}

	.timeline-item {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: var(--spacing-xl);
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
	}

	.timeline-marker {
		position: absolute;
		left: -15px;
		top: 0;
		width: 32px;
		height: 32px;
		background-color: var(--color-accent);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		border: 3px solid var(--color-background);
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.timeline-content {
		background-color: var(--color-surface);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: var(--spacing-lg);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.timeline-content:hover {
		transform: translateX(4px);
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.timeline-content h2 {
		margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.timeline-period {
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
	}

	.timeline-content p {
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}

	.learnings {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.learnings li {
		padding: var(--spacing-xs) 0;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		position: relative;
		padding-left: var(--spacing-md);
	}

	.learnings li::before {
		content: 'â†’';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.conclusion {
		background-color: var(--color-surface);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: var(--spacing-xl);
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
	}

	.conclusion h2 {
		margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.conclusion p {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	/* Additional styles for new sections */
	.mentors-section, .education-section, .mentor-highlight {
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
		padding: var(--spacing-md);
		background-color: var(--color-background);
		border-radius: 8px;
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
	}

	.mentors-section h3, .education-section h3, .mentor-highlight h3 {
		margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-sm);
		color: var(--color-text);
		font-size: 1.125rem;
	}

	.mentors {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.mentors li {
		padding: var(--spacing-xs) 0;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}

	.mentors a {
		color: var(--color-accent);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.mentors a:hover {
		color: var(--color-accent-hover);
	}

	.mentor-philosophy {
		font-style: italic;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-top: var(--spacing-sm);
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	.milestones {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0 0 var(--spacing-md) 0;
	}

	.milestones li {
		padding: var(--spacing-xs) 0;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		position: relative;
		padding-left: var(--spacing-md);
	}

	.milestones li::before {
		content: 'ðŸ“…';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
	}

	.core-focus {
		background-color: var(--color-surface);
